channel.title: Server won't run after power outtage
channel.description: There was a big storm in my area and it knocked out power for like 12 hours and my server obviously went down.. I tried to run it, it says server is online but it still says error connecting to server, I checked my ports with PfPortchecker and it says they are both open.. Please Help!

item.title: Server won't run after power outtage
item.dc:creator: @emo_skill emo skill
item.description:
@emo_skill wrote:

Yeah well I do have a Dynamic IP I have an Actiontec MI-424-WRv2 Router with Verizon ISP, but I reset my router config and re-portforward and the PfPortchecker still says they’re open ports, maybe my DNS server changed or something?
